Replace X's with your desired value.

00000000 = The damage caused by lightning doesn't reduce of size to the player, this effect deletes 
the lightning when it is thrown (only takes effect if you are in first place).

FFFFFFFF = The damage caused by lightning maintains reduced of size of the player, the only way to
return to normal size is using a bullet bill.

00020000 1051E740
